41
00:04:12,392 --> 00:04:16,294
Yeah, who?

42
00:04:16,496 --> 00:04:21,126
Just about
to land in WGV. Let's click on
the turnstiles on our wax files.

43
00:04:21,201 --> 00:04:23,465
- Ben?
- Yeah?

44
00:04:23,536 --> 00:04:26,835
- Are you mad?
- No.

45
00:04:26,906 --> 00:04:28,840
Well, baffled,
but not mad.

46
00:04:28,908 --> 00:04:31,706
I assume you had a good reason
for doing what you did.

47
00:04:31,778 --> 00:04:34,474
- The reason is that Joe went psycho.
- Shut up, Simon.

48
00:04:34,547 --> 00:04:36,481
That's a good reason as any.

49
00:04:36,549 --> 00:04:38,483
- It is?
- Sure.

50
00:04:38,551 --> 00:04:41,611
Everyone's got to reserve
the right to go a little nuts
every now and then.

51
00:04:41,688 --> 00:04:44,714
- Life isn't always so easy.
- Or fair.

52
00:04:44,791 --> 00:04:47,157
Oh, it's certainly not fair.

53
00:04:47,227 --> 00:04:49,161
Hey, you guys want to go get,

54
00:04:49,229 --> 00:04:51,754
uh, some pizza
or a hot dog or somethin'?

55
00:04:51,831 --> 00:04:55,198
- You want to take us for pizza?
